        "TileImage": "$($repository 4534ed4a-9018-45b4-bb85-0f2cfbc3f371).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening, 47. Your targets today are Emma and Patrick Carlisle, as well as one of the staff, Rosie Jones. The client wants Patrick and Emma Carlisle gone; Patrick for his womanizing behavior, and Emma for raising him this way. A &quot;stain&quot; on the Carlisle family, according to the client. He also wants Patrick&apos;s latest victim Rosie eliminated as well, for sympathizing with the pair.\r\rThe client asks that both Patrick and Rosie&apos;s death look like accidents, and for Emma to be poisoned. Good luck.",
